{"title":"Land Registry: Risk mitigation services for mortgage lenders","public_updated_at":"2016-12-15T15:05:53Z","details":{"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>As the definitive source of more than 24 million property titles for England and Wales, Land Registry safeguards property ownership worth over £4trillion, including over £1trillion of mortgages.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"charge-validation-service\">Charge validation service</h2>\n\n<p>We can help you keep up-to-date with your mortgage portfolio, by confirming the priority and status of your mortgages on the Register.</p>\n\n<p>If you are considering buying another firm’s back book, or have bought one, we can help you to conduct your due diligence.</p>\n\n<div class=\"call-to-action\">\n<p>Read more about our <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/land-registry-charge-validation-for-mortgage-lenders\">Charge validation service</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"data-sync-service\">Data sync service</h2>\n\n<p>This service allows you to synchronise your systems with ours, so that:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>you receive automatic notifications when your mortgages are registered or discharged</li>\n  <li>you know instantly when changes occur within your mortgage portfolio, helping you to detect risk at an early stage</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>There are extra options to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>electronically discharge your mortgages, to save you administration time and cost</li>\n  <li>confirm the priority of your mortgages, to help you meet lending criteria</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"call-to-action\">\n<p>Read more about our <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/land-registry-data-synch-for-mortgage-lenders\">Data sync service</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"other-services-for-lenders\">Other services for lenders</h2>\n\n<p>If you are a Business e-services customer, you can <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/lender-services\">discharge your mortgages online via the portal</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"more-information\">More information</h2>\n\n<p>To discuss your existing or future business needs, please contact us:</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact \" id=\"contact_2135\">\n  <div class=\"content\">\n    <h3>Business Development Fulfilment Team</h3>\n\n    <div class=\"vcard contact-inner\">\n\n        <div class=\"email-url-number\">\n            <p class=\"contact_form_url\">\n              <span class=\"type\">Contact form</span>\n              <a href=\"https://landregistry.custhelp.com/app/contactus_comm_services/\">https://landregistry.c...</a>\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"tel\">\n              <span class=\"type\">Phone</span>\n              0300 006 0478\n            </p>\n        </div>\n\n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</div>","change_history":[],"emphasised_organisations":["5c54ae52-341b-499e-a6dd-67f04633b8cf"],"related_mainstream_content":[],"national_applicability":{"england":{"label":"England","applicable":true},"northern_ireland":{"label":"Northern Ireland","applicable":false,"alternative_url":""},"scotland":{"label":"Scotland","applicable":false,"alternative_url":""},"wales":{"label":"Wales","applicable":true}},"political":false,"government":{"title":"2015 Conservative government","slug":"2015-conservative-government","current":true},"tags":{"browse_pages":[],"policies":[],"topics":[]},"first_public_at":"2016-12-15T15:05:53.000+00:00"},"routes":[{"path":"/guidance/land-registry-risk-mitigation-services-for-mortgage-lenders","type":"exact"}],"redirects":[],"publishing_app":"whitehall","rendering_app":"government-frontend","need_ids":[],"phase":"live","analytics_identifier":null,"document_type":"detailed_guide","schema_name":"detailed_guide","first_published_at":"2016-12-15T15:05:53Z","base_path":"/guidance/land-registry-risk-mitigation-services-for-mortgage-lenders","description":"Services for lenders and third parties working on their behalf that minimise mortgage risk and support due diligence.","content_id":"7c5f9cc3-0c3d-471e-8982-4bb5255a69b8","locale":"en","expanded_links":{"organisations"